      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything feels so empty now. i sat in the kitchen for three hours just staring at the wall because i realized i dont even know how to exist without them. ten years... and now it's like the sun isn't even coming up anymore. i just dont see the point in trying to get through tomorrow.",
